height and weight are used to create a box
border is used to add a border line and we can add specific values to border in clockwise direction
margin is used for outside space of a box
padding is used for creating inside space in a box

sample code

#a{
    height: 200px ;
    width: 200px;
    background-color: cadetblue;
    padding: 20px;
    border: 10px solid black;
}
#b{
    height: 200px ;
    width: 200px;
    background-color: gold;
    border: solid black;
    border-width: 20px 10px;
    margin-left: 260px;
}
#c{
    height: 200px ;
    width: 200px;
   background-color: indianred;
    border: 10px solid black;
    margin-left: 40px;
}
p{
    margin: 0px;
}
